text: Newly open and well stocked. Love their ready food!
Macdonald not yet 11pm but they already close the kiosk how to order.

The kiosk stall at bagus. Ordered a breakfast set about $3. I have no change so I gave $50. Even that moment she did not ask if I have smaller change but this Malay lady communicate with another lady saying that as if my food is $50 in Malay. As a customer we have in all. As a stall, they should have enough change to be given out and donâ€™t complaint about it. Teach them basic respect and how to communicate with customers.

Economic rice stall - order 2 vege, 1 meat, charge me $5.60, and costs me $5 after discount. Seller just key into machine as fish. See the pictures, I kid you not. Maybe MP for Bukit Panjang or Holland-Bukit Timah can look into it.
Typical small neighborhood shopping mall. Have a variety of shops and enrichment centers. Have 2 small foodcourt side by side (Kopitiam) but limit food selection as many stalls were closed down.
